<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 18:08:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 143 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-143/0000018d-e680-d47b-a1af-fef657660000</link><description>以色列代表团抵达卡塔尔参加人质释放协议谈判 ■ 以色列战时内阁批准援助直接进入加沙北部 ■ 以色列国防军表示，它在加沙地带找到了约 10 公里长的隧道系统 ■ 以色列未能遵守国际法院向加沙人提供援助的命令, 人权观察称 ■ 以色列国防军称真主党东部指挥部负责人 ■ 战争结束 143 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 17:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-143/0000018d-e680-d47b-a1af-fef657660000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列电视上，如果你胆敢提及占领，你就是反犹太主义者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-26/ty-article/.highlight/on-israeli-tv-youre-an-antisemite-if-you-dare-mention-the-occupation/0000018d-e60c-de64-afff-f67f1cee0000</link><description>以色列纪录片导演尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕周六在柏林国际电影节上发表的获奖感言《无他之地》被坎公共广播公司贴上了反犹太主义的标签。如今，任何提到事实的人都会被视为仇视犹太人</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 17:27:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-26/ty-article/.highlight/on-israeli-tv-youre-an-antisemite-if-you-dare-mention-the-occupation/0000018d-e60c-de64-afff-f67f1cee0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列情报机构在 10 月 7 日袭击发生前数小时检测到哈马斯激活的以色列 SIM 卡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-intel-detected-hundreds-of-israeli-sim-cards-activated-by-hamas-early-on-oct-7/0000018d-e5c3-dc4b-a1cd-f5efc8380000</link><description>这是异常活动的迹象，引发了高级国防官员在凌晨召开会议 ■ 普遍的评估称这是哈马斯演习 ■ 内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，以色列国防军称，以色列总理“直到现在才意识到这一点”卡在过去的事件中被激活</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 16:26:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-intel-detected-hundreds-of-israeli-sim-cards-activated-by-hamas-early-on-oct-7/0000018d-e5c3-dc4b-a1cd-f5efc8380000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将向国际法院提交报告，详细说明加沙地带的行动不构成种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-submit-report-to-icj-detailing-actions-in-gaza-strip-do-not-constitute-genocide/0000018d-e5b9-dc4b-a1cd-f5bd616e0000</link><description>在对南非针对以色列的种族灭绝案作出裁决后，向国际法院提交的报告预计将涉及人道主义义务和遵守法院临时命令的问题</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 15:23:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-submit-report-to-icj-detailing-actions-in-gaza-strip-do-not-constitute-genocide/0000018d-e5b9-dc4b-a1cd-f5bd616e0000</guid></item><item><title>当暴力主导阿以地方选举时，民主就会失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-violence-dominates-local-arab-israeli-elections-democracy-loses/0000018d-e52d-d596-a9ef-e7bf4ba20000</link><description>阿拉伯裔以色列公职人员越来越多地成为犯罪分子的目标，他们希望在周二的地方选举之前通过威胁、勒索和武力手段达到目的。竞选公职不应该让人们付出生命的代价</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 14:56:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-violence-dominates-local-arab-israeli-elections-democracy-loses/0000018d-e52d-d596-a9ef-e7bf4ba20000</guid></item><item><title>通过取消以色列奖，内塔尼亚胡的忠诚教育部长表现出了对更多的蔑视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/by-canceling-israel-prize-netanyahus-education-minister-showed-contempt-for-much-more/0000018d-e516-d596-a9ef-e7b749400000</link><description>教育部长约夫·基什取消了今年的大部分奖项，因为其中一位获奖者领导了反政府抗议活动，将以色列奖变成了他自己的私人企业</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 12:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/by-canceling-israel-prize-netanyahus-education-minister-showed-contempt-for-much-more/0000018d-e516-d596-a9ef-e7b749400000</guid></item><item><title>禁令、强烈反对和销售：有关以色列和巴勒斯坦的书籍正在抢购一空</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/books-on-israel-palestine-are-flying-off-the-shelves-and-shaking-up-the-literary-world/0000018d-e034-d47b-a1af-fe76bae20000</link><description>一本关于一名巴勒斯坦男孩的书被从新泽西学区的课程中删除，以及纽约一家书店的以色列-巴勒斯坦角落引起了世界的关注，这只是关于以色列和巴勒斯坦的书籍如何震撼出版界的两个例子，自 10 月 7 日以来，新的对话浮出水面</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 10:09:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/books-on-israel-palestine-are-flying-off-the-shelves-and-shaking-up-the-literary-world/0000018d-e034-d47b-a1af-fe76bae20000</guid></item><item><title>加沙和以色列，一个新词联想游戏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gaza-and-israel-a-new-word-association-game/0000018d-e0d2-df79-a5cd-e0fe41ef0000</link><description>广场上躺着他们的死者。令人印象深刻的战术成就。今天我们杀死了数十名恐怖分子。军队杀害了保护救援卡车免受抢劫的警察。它一直持续着</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 09:55:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gaza-and-israel-a-new-word-association-game/0000018d-e0d2-df79-a5cd-e0fe41ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院命令国家澄清为何不招募犹太学院学生加入以色列国防军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-hears-draft-law-petitions-as-protesters-call-for-equal-service/0000018d-e46b-d7f4-a3dd-e66f39fc0000</link><description>前摩萨德负责人参加了请愿活动，呼吁招募极端正统派人士来服务，他表示“没有一个国家可以在不分担负担的情况下存在”</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 09:18:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-hears-draft-law-petitions-as-protesters-call-for-equal-service/0000018d-e46b-d7f4-a3dd-e66f39fc0000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列等待哈马斯回应之际，内塔尼亚胡再次强硬立场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-waits-for-hamas-response-netanyahu-hardens-his-stance-again/0000018d-e230-d972-a5bf-eb374d740000</link><description>哈马斯关于人质谈判进展的积极迹象可能表明以色列军事压力的影响，以及协议可能导致战争结束 ■ 以色列警察的行为就好像他们是本格维尔警察，而不是仅限特拉维夫</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 03:56:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-waits-for-hamas-response-netanyahu-hardens-his-stance-again/0000018d-e230-d972-a5bf-eb374d740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击黎巴嫩纵深真主党目标；至少 60 枚火​​箭弹袭击以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article-live/israeli-team-to-head-to-qatar-for-talks-after-u-s-says-basic-contours-for-deal-reached/0000018d-e290-d596-a9ef-e3b39f2c0000</link><description>以色列代表团抵达卡塔尔参加人质交易谈判 ■ 以色列国防军证实暗杀了真主党东部司令部负责人 ■ 真主党称发射了 60 枚火​​箭弹以回应黎巴嫩的袭击 ■ 巴勒斯坦总理提交辞职 ■ 以色列允许援助直接进入加沙北部</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 03:49:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article-live/israeli-team-to-head-to-qatar-for-talks-after-u-s-says-basic-contours-for-deal-reached/0000018d-e290-d596-a9ef-e3b39f2c0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党需要加沙人质协议来决定其在黎巴嫩的政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-needs-a-hostage-deal-to-dictate-its-policies-in-lebanon/0000018d-e23b-d47b-a1af-fe7feec90000</link><description>纳斯鲁拉将与以色列的边境冲突与加沙战争联系起来的政策受到越来越多的反对，这意味着真主党领导人可能需要更多地集中精力重新完全控制黎巴嫩的政治进程，并为真正重要的运动做好准备——任命黎巴嫩真主党领导人。总统将维护该组织的地位及其武器</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 22:13:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-needs-a-hostage-deal-to-dictate-its-policies-in-lebanon/0000018d-e23b-d47b-a1af-fe7feec90000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争爆发两天后，以色列警察因殴打抗议者而受到讯问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officer-questioned-for-beating-a-protester-two-days-after-war-in-gaza-began/0000018d-e1fa-d596-a9ef-e3fb28400000</link><description>在示威期间拍摄的一段视频中，可以看到警长梅厄·苏伊萨(Meir Suissa)在特拉维夫基里亚综合大楼外推搡抗议者，其中包括一名年长的抗议者，他将其推倒在地</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 21:25:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officer-questioned-for-beating-a-protester-two-days-after-war-in-gaza-began/0000018d-e1fa-d596-a9ef-e3fb28400000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦权力机构以组建新政府为条件要求以色列撤军加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-authority-conditions-new-government-formation-to-israeli-gaza-withdrawal/0000018d-e1cb-d972-a5bf-ebcfa57a0000</link><description>巴解组织一直在讨论改变拉马拉政府的组成，以纳入哈马斯和其他组织。一位高级消息人士称，这一改变的条件包括“巴勒斯坦所有派系达成全国协议”以及以色列国防军停止对约旦河西岸城市的袭击</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 21:24:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-authority-conditions-new-government-formation-to-israeli-gaza-withdrawal/0000018d-e1cb-d972-a5bf-ebcfa57a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡要求驱逐“主要囚犯”；以色列高级官员猛烈抨击总理的“表现”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-demands-to-deport-major-prisoners-freed-top-official-slams-pms-performances/0000018d-e200-d596-a9ef-e3b33e470000</link><description>以色列高级消息人士称，内塔尼亚胡是在美国、卡塔尔和埃及提出提案后才提出驱逐要求的，这使得谈判变得复杂。他警告说，即使这是一种谈判策略，他的表现也可能会造成损害。</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 21:20:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-demands-to-deport-major-prisoners-freed-top-official-slams-pms-performances/0000018d-e200-d596-a9ef-e3b33e470000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列警察加大对人质家属的暴力力度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-25/ty-article/.highlight/why-israels-police-are-ramping-up-violence-against-the-families-of-hostages/0000018d-e17a-df79-a5cd-e17e595a0000</link><description>昨晚的抗议活动引人注目，不仅因为警察暴力的强度，还因为安全部队开始采取激进反应的速度。这标志着以色列抗议运动的一个重要转折点。但问题是：为了谁？</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 20:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-25/ty-article/.highlight/why-israels-police-are-ramping-up-violence-against-the-families-of-hostages/0000018d-e17a-df79-a5cd-e17e595a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布 10 月 7 日被带入加沙的以色列士兵死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/idf-announces-death-of-israeli-soldier-killed-on-oct-7-and-taken-into-gaza/0000018d-e1c1-d47b-a1af-fff723210000</link><description>10 月 7 日，装甲兵士兵奥兹·丹尼尔 (Oz Daniel) 驾驶的坦克被哈马斯击中身亡。他的尸体被哈马斯带入加沙地带，目前仍被哈马斯扣留。军队首席拉比在检查了允许按照哈拉卡埋葬的调查结果后确定了他的死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 19:59:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/idf-announces-death-of-israeli-soldier-killed-on-oct-7-and-taken-into-gaza/0000018d-e1c1-d47b-a1af-fff723210000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阻止西岸和加沙国际援助非政府组织工作人员的工作签证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-blocks-work-visas-from-international-aid-ngo-workers-in-west-bank-and-gaza/0000018d-e195-df79-a5cd-e1bfa8600000</link><description>这种拒绝扰乱了许多参与向加沙居民提供医疗援助、食品和水的机构的运作，这些居民主要受到严重饥饿和脱水的影响。一些援助人员告诉国土报，他们担心这一决定背后有政治动机</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 19:38:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-blocks-work-visas-from-international-aid-ngo-workers-in-west-bank-and-gaza/0000018d-e195-df79-a5cd-e1bfa8600000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡不是泽伦斯基。但他们确实有一个共同点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/as-war-in-ukraine-hits-a-milestone-zelenskyy-and-netanyahu-adapt-to-shifting-geopolitics/0000018d-e127-dc4b-a1cd-f12f943a0000</link><description>俄罗斯入侵乌克兰两周年是基辅和更远地区进行深刻反省的阴沉时刻。尽管几乎不可能比较乌克兰战争和以色列加沙战争，但以色列仍然应该吸收其中的战略影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 18:30:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/as-war-in-ukraine-hits-a-milestone-zelenskyy-and-netanyahu-adapt-to-shifting-geopolitics/0000018d-e127-dc4b-a1cd-f12f943a0000</guid></item><item><title>周二在密歇根州举行的民主党初选成为对拜登加沙战争立场的公投</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tuesdays-democratic-primary-in-michigan-becomes-referendum-on-bidens-gaza-war-stance/0000018d-e07c-d596-a9ef-e3ff41ee0000</link><description>由于密歇根州拥有规模庞大的阿拉伯裔美国人和穆斯林裔美国人社区，美国总统乔·拜登将了解他自 10 月 7 日以来的行动可能会对他 11 月连任的机会产生多大影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 18:16:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tuesdays-democratic-primary-in-michigan-becomes-referendum-on-bidens-gaza-war-stance/0000018d-e07c-d596-a9ef-e3ff41ee0000</guid></item></channel></rss>